content: Loved it. Very much improved since I last used it but now I can say it's really useful app and services. Great experience so far. .A few suggestions: Please see if you could comeup with BharatQR instead of simple UPI QR. Also if payer could see the company name instead of BharatPe Merchant in UPI app. Right now BharatQR app doesn't work with current QR but I believe UPI payments is also possible with BharatQR format.
